					<p>The group‘s task is daunting: it must tackle the problem of interoperability of different data types on each of the major crops (germplasm data, genetic and phenotype data, statistical data, text). (<a href="http://voa3r.eu/news-events/news/174-constitution-of-agricultural-data-interest-group-within-rda?utm_source=K4DNewsletterEN&amp;utm_medium=Link&amp;utm_campaign=K4D_EN_April2013" target="_self">Voa3r</a>, 12/04/2013)</p>
